@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_uvprhb(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.abs(0.46))
    v2 = (0.65 * ((tmp + 0.76 + tmp + 0.73) / wp.abs(v2 + 0.45)))
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.abs(tmp))
    v1 = wp.abs(wp.exp((v1 + 0.01 - v1 + 0.93)))
    tmp = 0.23
    v1 = tmp
    v0 = 0.26
    v2 = v1
    data[tid] = v0
